    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200\u00b0C/ 180\u00b0C (fan)/ 395\u00b0F/ Gas 6</p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Top, tail and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cheese-fondue-charcuterie-and-alpine-salad/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop the root<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the<strong> little gem lettuce</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and tear the <strong>leaves</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces and give them a wash</p><p>Combine the<strong> red wine vinegar</strong> with the<strong> Dijon mustard</strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>\u2013 this is your<strong> vinaigrette</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cheese-fondue-charcuterie-and-alpine-salad/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>torn little gem</strong> to a serving bowl and top with the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and <strong>grated carrot</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>Alpine salad</strong></p><p>Set aside for serving</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cheese-fondue-charcuterie-and-alpine-salad/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>ciabatta rolls</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until hot and crusty</p><p>Once done, carefully cut the ciabatta rolls into bite-sized cubes</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cheese-fondue-charcuterie-and-alpine-salad/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>For fancy presentation, cut the <strong>peppered salami </strong>in half and roll each half into cone-shapes</p><p>Tip: Too fiddly? Just break both up into smaller pieces!</p><p>Add the the <strong>Serrano ham</strong>, <strong>Napoli salami</strong> and<strong> salami cones</strong> to a serving board or plate \u2013 this is your<strong> charcuterie</strong></p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cheese-fondue-charcuterie-and-alpine-salad/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced garlic</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Cut the <strong>cheese fondue packet<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> open and squeeze into the pot (as much as you can!)</p><p>Cook for 6-8 min, stirring continuously until melted and silky</p><p>Tip: Although it melts quickly, letting it bubble for longer cooks off any excess alcohol!</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cheese-fondue-charcuterie-and-alpine-salad/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>cornichons</strong> to a small serving bowl</p><p>Once everything's ready to serve, dress the <strong>Alpine salad</strong> with the <strong>vinaigrette</strong></p><p>Season the melted cheese with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>cheese fondue</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/cheese-fondue-charcuterie-and-alpine-salad/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cheese fondue</strong>, <strong>ciabatta cubes</strong>, <strong>charcuterie</strong>, <strong>cornichons </strong>and <strong>Alpine salad </strong>in the centre of the table, ready to share</p><p>Let everyone dig in</p><p>Tip: You may need to reheat the cheese every so often to keep it super melty</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
